topBadges.name: Boat Shoe (5,000 steps in a day)
topBadges.shareText: I took 5,000 steps and earned the Boat Shoe badge! #Fitbit
topBadges.earnedMessage: Congrats on earning your first Boat Shoe badge!
topBadges.mobileDescription: Congratulations on cruising your way to the first Fitbit daily step badge.
topBadges.marketingDescription: You've walked 5,000 steps And earned the Boat Shoe badge!

topBadges.name: Urban Boot (15,000 steps in a day)
topBadges.shareText: I took 15,000 steps and earned the Urban Boot badge! #Fitbit
topBadges.earnedMessage: Congrats on earning your first Urban Boot badge!
topBadges.mobileDescription: With a number that's almost three times more than the national average, your step count is really heating up.
topBadges.marketingDescription: You've walked 15,000 steps  And earned the Urban Boot badge!

topBadges.name: Penguin March (70 lifetime miles)
topBadges.shareText: I covered 70 miles with my #Fitbit and earned the Penguin March badge.
topBadges.earnedMessage: Whoa! You've earned the Penguin March badge!
topBadges.mobileDescription: You matched the distance of the March of the Penguins—the annual trip emperor penguins make to their breeding grounds.
topBadges.marketingDescription: By reaching 70 lifetime miles, you've earned the Penguin March badge!
